  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "A honest proposer should pick deposit from contract logs and add it to the beacon block body to propose when it's his/her slot.\r\n\r\nA rational proposer may not do that without proper incentives, the proposer could simply stop on boarding new validators, locking out new comers through self interest or just laziness.\r\n\r\nI wonder if proposer should be rewarded for deposit inclusion and maybe penalized(?) for not including existed deposits?",
